text: Camila is the debut solo album by Cuban American singer Camila Cabello. She was previously a member of the girl group Fifth Harmony. The album was released on January 12, 2018. Camila entered the US Billboard 200 album chart at number one, with 119,000 copies and streaming units sold in its first week. It reached number one in the same week as the single "Havana". As a result, she became only the third artist in history to have their first album and one of its singles both reach number one in the same week.
